sql:
SELECT category_name
FROM area_categories
WHERE color_code = '#4CAF50';

SELECT category_id, COUNT(area_id) AS area_count, AVG(confidence) AS average_confidence
FROM geographical_areas
GROUP BY category_id;

external_knowledge:
The top 3 most frequented territories refer to those with the highest number of access counts; 
Territories include various geographical areas such as national parks, cities, and monuments; 
Descriptions include the category names of these areas; 
Accuracy scores refer to the confidence levels indicating the reliability of the data, ranging from 0.0 to 1.0.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS compliant_areas_count
FROM geographical_areas
WHERE compliance_status = 'Compliant';
